; nl-neutral-trace-sweep-live.fk — THE single command that sweeps all 10,000
; concept rows into the persisted nodeid-rag-v2 index and witnesses queries
; through the production disk path:
;
;     ./fkwu --src cognition/tests/nl-neutral-trace-sweep-live.fk
;
; Takes a few minutes once; progress prints every 500 rows. Afterward the
; main trace command answers every query from this index.
;
; Expected loud line: ONE [unresolved-call] (form-ontology-loader.fk's
; walk_recipe_here, kept loud there on purpose). See nl-neutral-trace.fk.
;
